Laura added, "My goal is to ensure that no woman ever suffers [this kind of abuse](https://www.foxnews.com/category/entertainment/events/scandal) from him again. I want to send the message that women are victims and survivors, not perpetrators or guilty parties."

 ![Enrique Iglesias](https://a57.foxnews.com/static.foxnews.com/foxnews.com/content/uploads/2026/01/1200/675/enrique.jpg?ve=1&tl=1)

Julio Iglesias is the father of Enrique Iglesias. (Getty Images)

Iglesias, the father of famed singer Enrique Iglesias, is a two-time [Grammy-winning](https://www.foxnews.com/category/entertainment/events/grammys) artist. He has been inducted into the Latin Songwriters Hall of Fame.

